task.summary: Updated version. Updated build target. Replaced ActionbarSherlock with AppCompat. Added GDP, income and economy sectors.
Fixed bugs with new design and news section.
Fixed bug with instant issues. Added regional officers.
Fixed bug with dossier and missing home region id at start. Added current census rank to nation page.
Implemented HTTPS for logged in features. Added World section with search. Added "next issue" time for issues.
Added delegate and founder to officers list.
Added auto-checking of new issues. Added founder and delegate to officers list.
